criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. age >18 years;

          2. no history of surgical treatment or radiotherapy;

          3. no preoperative paralysis;

          4. no contraindications to the magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) scan;

          5. distance from the tumor to the hand knob area < 20 mm;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. patients can not tolerate awake craniotomy and intraoperative brain mapping

          2. head motion is greater than 3 mm during functional MRI scanning
